response.original_title: King Stays King: Sold Out at Madison Square Garden
response.overview: This concert film captures an eighteen song, 2012 set from Romeo, as he played a sold out Madison Square Garden show during his first solo tour after leaving Aventura. The setlist includes "Malevo," "Soberbio," and "Vale La Pena El Placer."
response.title: King Stays King: Sold Out at Madison Square Garden
